title: NFL extends deal to play games at Wembley through 2020
text:
> Top News NFL extends deal to play games at Wembley through 2020 Buffalo Bills quarterback EJ Manuel smiles during a press conference after an NFL training session at the Grove Hotel in Chandler's Cross, England, Thursday, Oct. 22, 2015. The Buffalo Bills play the Jacksonville Jaguars at Wembley stadium in London on Sunday in a regular season NFL game. (AP Photo/Matt Dunham)
